---
// src/components/Features.astro
---
<section id="nosotros" class="bg-[#F9FAFB] py-16 lg:py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-7xl">
    
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-titulo font-bold text-center text-[#183153] mb-16 lg:mb-24">
      ¿Qué puedes esperar de nosotros?
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center relative">

      <div class="order-1 flex flex-col gap-12 lg:gap-24 w-full">
        
        <div class="group flex items-center lg:justify-end relative">
          <div class="text-left lg:text-right max-w-xs lg:pr-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Agilidad</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Somos una compañía atenta e informada, reaccionamos rápido para adaptarnos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -right-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group flex items-center lg:justify-end relative">
          <div class="text-left lg:text-right max-w-xs lg:pr-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Vanguardismo</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Somos modernos y tratamos de ir siempre un paso adelante en tendencias.
            </p>
          </div>
           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -right-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="order-2 flex justify-center relative z-10 py-8 lg:py-0">
        <div class="relative w-64 h-80 lg:w-80 lg:h-[500px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border-4 border-white">
            <img src="/images/TelaNosotros.png" 
               alt="Rollos de tela" 
               class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#8b9e8d]/10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="order-3 flex flex-col gap-12 lg:gap-24 w-full">
        
        <div class="group flex items-center lg:justify-start relative">
           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -left-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div> 
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div> 
          </div>
          <div class="text-left max-w-xs lg:pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Rapidez</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Realiza tu pedido y recíbelo con la eficiencia logística que necesitas.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group flex items-center lg:justify-start relative">
           <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center absolute -left-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2">
             <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
             <div class="w-16 h-[1px] bg-[#8b9e8d]"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-left max-w-xs lg:pl-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-titulo font-bold text-[#183153] mb-2">Arquitectura Sólida</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Tienes a todo el equipo de T3 detrás tuyo para asegurar el éxito.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>